<Layout title="Roadmap">
  <h1 class="page-title">Roadmap</h1>
  <div class="card">
    <p>Upcoming milestones focus on keeping the spec minimal, explicit, and forward-compatible.</p>
    <h2>v0.1.0 delivered</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Published the first stable OpenTab specification with explicit semantics.</li>
      <li>Documented core parsing rules to keep timing deterministic and formatting non-semantic.</li>
      <li>Provided focused samples and tooling references to help teams adopt the format.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Upcoming</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>v0.2: Clarify timing semantics and add more sample coverage.</li>
      <li>v0.3: Expand tooling references and refine validation guidance.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>
